🔷 11. ENGINE REUSABILITY MODEL

The engine is shared infrastructure.
Features configure it — they do not reimplement it.

Shared Engine Primitives:

UI:
  RecordViewShell
  SectionShell
  FieldSection (shared field layout)
  GridSection (shared grid layout)
  ChildScopedRowShell

Controllers:
  useRecordController
  useSectionController (FieldSection)
  useGridSectionController (GridSection)
  useChildScopedRowController
  useReconciliation
  useWorkflowPolling

Features plug in:
  section config (type, fields, columns)
  domain-specific validators
  domain-specific API endpoints
  domain-specific labels

